      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for this. it's a good start but it feels a little too generic/standard. could you try to make it a bit more personal? maybe add a sentence or two acknowledging that they specifically crushed the technical portion of the interview so they know we actually valued their skill level. just keep it professional though.",
